---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="False Prophets — The Priesthood — Nazaryah"
  description="Yahushua did not warn about atheists or pagans. He warned about wolves in sheep's clothing. The modern megachurch movement is the most visible expression of that warning."
>
  <div class="al-wrap">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="al-hero">
      <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/the-institutional-church" class="al-back">&#8592; Back to The Institutional Church</a>
      <p class="al-label">&#8213; The Priesthood · Full Study &#8213;</p>
      <h1 class="al-title">False Prophets</h1>
      <p class="al-sub">
        Wolves in Sheep's Clothing
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── ARTICLE BODY ── -->
    <article class="al-article">
      <div class="al-inner">

        <blockquote class="al-quote">
          <p class="al-quote-ref">Matthew 7:15</p>
          <p>"Beware of false prophets, which come to you in sheep's clothing, but inwardly they are ravening wolves."</p>
        </blockquote>

        <div class="al-prose">
          <p>
            Yahushua did not say "beware of atheists." He did not say "beware of pagans." He said beware of people who come to you dressed as believers. Sheep's clothing. The warning was always about the inside of the house, not the outside.
          </p>
          <p>
            The modern megachurch movement is the most visible expression of this warning. Pastors with private jets, multimillion-dollar mansions, and celebrity platforms stand before congregations of thousands and preach a gospel that bears no resemblance to the words of Yahushua. Prosperity theology teaches that financial wealth is a sign of Yahuah's favor — a doctrine that would have been unrecognizable to the apostles who were imprisoned, beaten, and killed for their testimony.
          </p>
          <p>
            The names are well-known. Kenneth Copeland. Joel Osteen. Creflo Dollar. Benny Hinn. Todd White. These men and others like them draw massive followings, collect enormous wealth, and teach doctrines that directly contradict the Torah, the prophets, and the words of the Messiah. They are not anomalies. They are the product of a system that was designed from the ground up to replace the authority of Scripture with the authority of men.
          </p>
        </div>

        <blockquote class="al-quote">
          <p class="al-quote-ref">2 Timothy 4:3&#8211;4</p>
          <p>"For the time will come when they will not endure sound doctrine; but after their own lusts shall they heap to themselves teachers, having itching ears; And they shall turn away their ears from the truth, and shall be turned unto fables."</p>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="al-quote al-quote-closing">
          <p class="al-quote-ref">Matthew 7:15</p>
          <p>"Beware of false prophets, which come to you in sheep's clothing, but inwardly they are ravening wolves."</p>
        </blockquote>

        <div class="al-seal">&#10022; &nbsp; &#10022; &nbsp; &#10022;</div>

      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- ── BACK BUTTON ── -->
    <section class="al-footer-nav">
      <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/the-institutional-church" class="al-back-btn">&#8592; Back to The Institutional Church</a>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .al-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0e0904 0%, #1a1208 20%, #160f07 100%);
    color: #f0e0bf;
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .al-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #4a3218;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(180, 100, 20, 0.18), transparent 65%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0602 0%, #1a1208 100%);
  }

  .al-back {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #6a4820;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .al-back:hover { color: #c4a46b; }

  .al-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #8a6028;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .al-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f0e0bf;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .al-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.15rem);
    color: #c4a46b;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .al-article { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
  .al-inner { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .al-prose {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #d9c9a8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .al-prose p { margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
  .al-prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .al-prose em { color: #c4a46b; font-style: italic; }
  .al-prose strong { color: #e8d5a8; font-weight: 600; }

  .al-quote {
    margin: 1.75rem 0;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem 1.25rem 1.75rem;
    border-left: 3px solid #7a4a18;
    background: rgba(10, 6, 2, 0.4);
    border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
  }
  .al-quote p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #c4ad84;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .al-quote-ref {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px !important;
    font-style: normal !important;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #8a5a28 !important;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
  }

  .al-quote-closing {
    border-left-color: #c4a46b;
    background: rgba(186, 117, 23, 0.05);
  }

  .al-seal {
    text-align: center;
    color: #6a4820;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 8px;
    margin: 3rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .al-footer-nav {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #2e1f0d;
  }

  .al-back-btn {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #6a4820;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .al-back-btn:hover { color: #c4a46b; }
</style>
